cs - Men's discus throw}}\n[[Category:Athletics at the 1976 Summer Olympics|T]]\n[[Category:Discus throw at the Olympics]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox Olympic event\n|event = Men's discus throw\n|games = 1976 Summer\n|image =\n|caption =\n|date = {{Date|1976-7-24}} (qualifications)<br />{{Date|1976-7-25}} (final)\n|venue = [[Olympic Stadium (Montreal)|Olympic Stadium]]\n|competitors = 30\n|nations = 20\n|win_label = Winning distance\n|win_value = 67.50\n|longnames = yes\n|gold = [[Mac Wilkins]]\n|goldNOC = USA\n|silver = [[Wolfgang Schmidt]]\n|silverNOC = GDR\n|bronze = [[John Powell (athlete)|John Powell]]\n|bronzeNOC = USA\n|prev = [[Athletics at the 1972 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's discus throw|1972]]\n|next = [[Athletics at the 1980 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's discus throw|1980]]\n}}\n{{AthleticsAt1976SummerOlympics}}\nThe '''[[Discus throw|Men's Discus Throw]]''' event at the '''[[Athletics at the 1976 Summer Olympics|1976 Summer Olympics]]''' in [[Montreal|Montreal, Quebec]], [[Canada]] had an entrylist of 30 competitors, with two qualifying groups (30 jumpers) before the final (15) took place on Sunday July 25, 1976. The top twelve and ties, and all those reaching 60.00 metres advanced to the final. The qualification round was held in Saturday July 24, 1976.<ref name=\"SR\">{{cite web |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/1976/ATH/mens-discus-throw.html |title=Athletics at the 1976 Montreal Summer Games: Men's Discus Throw |accessdate=13 January 2018 |work=sports-reference.com}}</ref>\n\n==Medalists==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\" text-align:center; font-size:110%;\" width=\"35%\"\n|- \n|{{OlympicGoldMedalist|[[Mac Wilkins]]|USA|1976 Summer}}\n|-\n|{{OlympicSilverMedalist|[[Wolfgang Schmidt]]|GDR|1976 Summer}}\n|-\n|{{OlympicBronzeMedalist|[[John Powell (athlete)|John Powell]]|USA|1976 Summer}}\n|}\n\n==Abbreviations==\n*''All results shown are in metres''\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\" text-align:center; font-size:110%;\" width=\"35%\"\